'''马歇尔·A·伯特'''（{{lang-en|Marshall A. Burt }}，{{bd|1976年|5月6日}}）是美国政治家、轨道检查员和退伍军人，自2021年以来任职于[[怀俄明州众议院|怀俄明州众议院]]，代表{{le|怀俄明州众议院第三十九选区|Wyoming House of Representatives 39th district|第三十九选区}}。他是[[自由意志党|自由意志党]]的成员。

伯特出生于[[明尼苏达州|明尼苏达州]][[罗彻斯特_(明尼苏达州)|罗切斯特]]，是[[美国海军陆战队|海军陆战队]]退伍军人，是自2000年{{le|史蒂夫·维兰科特|Steve Vaillancourt}}以来第一个以自由意志党人身份当选州议会议员的人。他也是100多年来第一位成功当选的{{le|怀俄明州议会|Wyoming Legislature}}[[第三党_(美国)|第三党]]候选人。

==怀俄明州众议院==
===选举===
在{{le|2020年怀俄明州众议院选举|2020 Wyoming House of Representatives election}}中，共有六位在竞争激烈选区竞选的{{le|怀俄明州自由意志党|Libertarian Party of Wyoming}}候选人，伯特便是其中之一<ref>{{Cite web|last=Reynolds|first=Nick|date=2020-11-04|title=Green River candidate becomes first Libertarian to win statehouse seat anywhere in U.S. since 2002|url=https://trib.com/news/state-and-regional/govt-and-politics/green-river-candidate-becomes-first-libertarian-to-win-statehouse-seat-anywhere-in-u-s-since/article_8c763a39-31d5-58e9-849e-3f13489b9a19.html|dead-url=no|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2021-04-09|website=Casper Star-Tribune Online|language=en}}</ref>。伯特参选第三十九选区，在一场两人竞争中，伯特击败了他的[[民主党_(美国)|民主党]]对手——长期在任的{{le|斯坦·布莱克|Stan Blake}}，伯特获得了54.4%的选票，布莱克获得了45.6%的选票<ref>{{Cite web|last=Doherty|first=Brian|date=2020-11-04|title=Libertarian Candidate Marshall Burt Wins Wyoming State House Race|url=https://reason.com/2020/11/04/libertarian-candidate-marshall-burt-wins-wyoming-state-house-race/|dead-url=no|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2021-04-08|website=Reason|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Wyoming State House - District 39 Election Results <nowiki>|</nowiki> The Arizona Republic|url=https://www.azcentral.com/elections/results/race/2020-11-03-state-house-WY-51377/|website=azcentral.com|language=en|accessdate=2021-04-08}}</ref>。

===任期===
2021年3月，伯特提出了一项法案，以更改所有州[[大选|大选]][[选票|选票]]中候选人的顺序<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://ballot-access.org/2021/03/05/wyoming-bill-revising-order-of-candidates-on-ballot-passes-committee/ |title = Wyoming Bill, Revising Order of Candidates on Ballot, Passes Committee|website=Ballot Access News |author = Richard Winger|date = 2021-03-05 |language = en|accessdate = 2021-04-08}}</ref>。该法案详细规定，[[候选人|候选人]]在选票上的顺序将基于他们的姓名，来自字母[[彩票|彩票系统]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://legiscan.com/WY/text/HB0160/2021&ved=2ahUKEwj9n9mwhtDvAhXGaM0KHTIqAjQQFjABegQIBRAC&usg=AOvVaw1TaE4Wl0ZOPU-3JiZCVmY_&cshid=1616833924805 |title = Wyoming House Bill 160|website=LegiScan |language = en|accessdate = 2021-04-09}}</ref>。该系统使候选人随机出现在选票上，每一次选举都会改变。目前的选票顺序是根据候选人在初选中获得的选票，从最高到最低<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://fastdemocracy.com/bill-search/wy/2021/bills/WYB00003443/ |title = HB 160|website=FastDemocracy |language = en|accessdate = 2021-04-09}}</ref>。

就在同一个月，伯特与{{le|两党合作|Bipartisanship|两党}}的众议员共同发起了一项法案，该法案将使任何21岁以上[[怀俄明州|怀俄明州]]公民的{{le|美国管辖范围内大麻的合法性|Legality of cannabis by U.S. jurisdiction|大麻销售、购买、持有和种植合法化}}。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://cannabisindustryjournal.com/news_article/wyoming-lawmakers-introduce-bill-to-legalize-cannabis/ |title = Wyoming Lawmakers Introduce Bill to Legalize Cannabis|website=Cannabis Industry Journal|date = 2021-03-03 |language = en|accessdate = 2021-04-09}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://buckrail.com/bill-proposing-regulation-of-marijuana-in-wyoming/ |title = Bill proposes regulation of marijuana in Wyoming, $30.7 million per year to school fund|website=Buckrail|date = 2021-03-03 |language = en|accessdate = 2021-04-09}}</ref>

==政治立场==
===枪支政策===
伯特是[[持枪权|枪支权利]]的支持者，他反对增加[[枪支管制|枪支管制]]法规。伯特反对所有枪支登记或即时背景调查，并呼吁“在怀俄明州，无论是公开携带还是隐藏携带，都不需要许可证或居住证。”<ref name="Burt website positions">{{Cite web|url=https://burtforliberty.com/second-amendment/|title=Second Amendment|website=Representative Marshall Burt | Wyoming House 39|access-date=2021-04-09|language=en}}</ref>

