==个人生活==
伯特出生在[[明尼苏达州|明尼苏达州]]的[[罗彻斯特_(明尼苏达州)|罗切斯特]]，他与妻子特蕾莎·伯特住在怀俄明州的[[绿河_(怀俄明州)|绿河]]。伯特是[[美国海军陆战队|美国海军陆战队]]退伍军人，曾在日本[[冲绳县|冲绳]]和[[伊拉克战争|伊拉克战争]]中服役9年<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.legion.org/membership/227976/resurrection-green-river |title = The Resurrection of Green River|website=The American Legion
 |author = Ken Olsen|date = 2015-06-01 |language = en|accessdate = 2021-04-09}}</ref>。伯特退伍之后受雇于[[联合太平洋铁路|联合太平洋铁路]]担任轨道检查员。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Reynolds|first=Nick|date=2020-11-05|title=Burt first third-party candidate to win Wyoming race in more than 100 years|url=https://www.gillettenewsrecord.com/news/wyoming/article_55bf3092-b7e7-5dad-bddc-6d71fd66939a.html|dead-url=no|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2021-04-09|website=Gillette News Record|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-11-05|title=Meet Marshall Burt, Who's About To Become the Libertarian Party's Only Sitting State Legislator|url=https://reason.com/2020/11/05/meet-marshall-burt-whos-about-to-become-the-libertarian-partys-only-sitting-state-legislator/|access-date=2021-04-09|website=Reason|language=en}}</ref>

伯特的左前臂上有一个纹身，与[[反国家主义|反政府]]和[[极右翼|极右翼]]{{le|美国民兵运动|American militia movement|民兵运动}}“{{le|百分之三人|Three Percenters}}”有关<ref>{{Cite web|last=Rohrlich|first=Justin|date=2021-03-05|title=Wyoming State Rep. Under Fire for Three Percenter Tattoo|url=https://www.thedailybeast.com/libertarian-rep-marshall-burt-of-wyoming-under-fire-for-three-percenter-militia-tattoo|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-04-09|website=The Daily Beast|language=en}}</ref>。伯特否认与该组织有关联，回应说他“纹身是因为[[美国革命|美国革命]]的象征意义吸引了我，对我来说，它代表了我对[[美国宪法第二修正案|第二修正案]]和[[美国宪法第十修正案|第十修正案]]的坚定承诺<ref name="WyoFile 2021">{{cite web|last=Reynolds|first=Nick|date=2021-03-04|title=New lawmaker’s tattoo has ties to far-right anti-government movement|url=https://www.wyofile.com/new-lawmakers-tattoo-has-ties-to-far-right-anti-government-movement/|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-04-09|website=WyoFile|language=en}}</ref>。

